Parasite
===
4
===
2 March 2030
===
A tick that feeds on bloated corpses
A leech that sucks out life
A tapeworm feeding on your love and morals
For the butterfly we strife.

The cold machine stomps on and on
Buries what it doesn t need
And yet we toil and toil away
For the endless centipede

Another step, again we crush
Defile, disgrace, and lay to waste
A parasite, that we all serve
Now back to work we go with haste